---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import LocationMap from '../components/LocationMap.jsx';
---

<Layout
	title="Preston Speaking Club - Toastmasters"
	description="Transform your speaking skills and leadership abilities at Preston Speaking Club. A Toastmasters organisation dedicated to empowering members through communication development in a supportive environment."
	url="/"
>
	<!-- Important Notice Banner - Fixed at top -->
	<div class="fixed w-full top-0 z-50 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-yellow-400 text-gray-900 py-3 px-4 shadow-lg border-b-4 border-amber-500">
		<div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
			<svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
				<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
			</svg>
			<p class="text-center font-semibold text-sm md:text-base">
				<span class="font-bold">Important Notice:</span> There will be no meeting on 1st January 2026. Our next meeting will be on the 16th January 2026.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<Header />

	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4 bg-preston-blue text-white overflow-hidden">
		<!-- Video Background -->
		<video
			autoplay
			loop
			muted
			playsinline
			class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
		>
			<source src="/hero-video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
		</video>

		<!-- Dark overlay for better text readability -->
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-preston-blue opacity-60"></div>

		<div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center relative z-10 py-20">
			<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
				Discover the Potential of <span class="text-yellow-300">Effective Communication</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 text-white">
				Transform your speaking skills and leadership abilities at Preston Speaking Club
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
				<a
					href="#meetings"
					class="bg-white text-preston-blue px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-preston-blue-50 transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1"
				>
					Visit a Meeting
				</a>
				<a
					href="#about"
					class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-preston-blue transition-all duration-200"
				>
					Learn More
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- About Section -->
	<section id="about" class="py-20 px-4 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
			<div class="text-center mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">About Preston Speaking Club</h2>
				<div class="w-24 h-1 bg-preston-blue mx-auto"></div>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
				<div>
					<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
						We are a Toastmasters organisation dedicated to empowering our members through the development of communication and leadership skills in a supportive, engaging environment.
					</p>
					<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
						Whether you're preparing for interviews, delivering presentations, or simply want to feel more confident in social situations, Preston Speaking Club provides the perfect platform for growth.
					</p>
					<div class="flex items-start space-x-3 mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
						</svg>
						<p class="text-gray-700">All skill levels welcome - from beginners to experienced speakers</p>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start space-x-3 mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
						</svg>
						<p class="text-gray-700">Supportive, friendly environment focused on personal growth</p>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
						</svg>
						<p class="text-gray-700">Part of Toastmasters International - the world leader in communication training</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-preston-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Who Benefits?</h3>
					<div class="space-y-4">
						<div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-preston-blue mb-2">Job Seekers</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Master interview skills and present yourself with confidence</p>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-preston-blue mb-2">Professionals</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Deliver compelling presentations and lead with authority</p>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-preston-blue mb-2">Anyone</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Build social confidence and communicate effectively in any setting</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Membership Benefits Section -->
	<section id="membership" class="py-20 px-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
			<div class="text-center mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why Join Us?</h2>
				<div class="w-24 h-1 bg-preston-blue mx-auto mb-6"></div>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
					Unlock your potential and achieve your communication goals
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-preston-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-preston-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Transform</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Build confidence, develop leadership skills, and become an effective communicator through regular practice and constructive feedback.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Network</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Connect with like-minded individuals from diverse backgrounds and build lasting relationships in a supportive community.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Grow</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Advance your career with improved presentation skills, critical thinking, and the ability to lead and inspire others.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Meetings Section -->
	<section id="meetings" class="py-20 px-4 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
			<div class="text-center mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Join Our Meetings</h2>
				<div class="w-24 h-1 bg-preston-blue mx-auto"></div>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
				<div>
					<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-preston-blue to-preston-blue-800 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl mb-8">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Meeting Schedule</h3>
						<div class="space-y-4">
							<div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 2a1 1 0 00-1 1v1H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-1V3a1 1 0 10-2 0v1H7V3a1 1 0 00-1-1zm0 5a1 1 0 000 2h8a1 1 0 100-2H6z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold">When</p>
									<p class="text-preston-blue-100">1st and 3rd Thursday of each month</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-12a1 1 0 10-2 0v4a1 1 0 00.293.707l2.828 2.829a1 1 0 101.415-1.415L11 9.586V6z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold">Time</p>
									<p class="text-preston-blue-100">6:30 PM - 8:45 PM</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold">Location</p>
									<p class="text-preston-blue-100">Caritas Care Plungington Community Centre</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
						<h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
							</svg>
							Accessibility
						</h4>
						<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
							Our venue is fully accessible with wheelchair access, disabled parking, and accessible facilities. We're committed to ensuring everyone can participate comfortably.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg h-[450px]">
					<LocationMap client:load />
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Venue Photos -->
			<div class="mt-12">
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">Our Venue</h3>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
					<div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
						<img
							src="/community-centre-front.webp"
							alt="Plungington Community Centre - Front entrance with distinctive church tower"
							class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
							loading="lazy"
						/>
						<div class="bg-white p-4">
							<p class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">Community Centre Entrance</p>
							<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Easy to find with the iconic church tower</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
						<img
							src="/community-centre-back.webp"
							alt="Plungington Community Centre - Building exterior view"
							class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
							loading="lazy"
						/>
						<div class="bg-white p-4">
							<p class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">Community Centre Building</p>
							<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Accessible and welcoming facilities</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- FAQ Section -->
	<section id="faq" class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
		<div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
			<div class="text-center mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
				<div class="w-24 h-1 bg-preston-blue mx-auto"></div>
			</div>

			<div class="space-y-4">
				<details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
					<summary class="cursor-pointer p-6 font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-between">
						<span>What is Toastmasters</span>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-preston-blue transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						<p class="mb-4">Toastmasters is an international organisation that helps people develop their public speaking and leadership skills through a network of local clubs that follow a program of regular meetings, speeches, and evaluations.</p>
						<a href="https://www.toastmasters.org" class="text-preston-blue hover:underline font-semibold">Find out more</a>
					</div>
				</details>

				<details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
					<summary class="cursor-pointer p-6 font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-between">
						<span>How often do Preston Speaking Club meetings take place?</span>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-preston-blue transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Meetings for Preston Speaking Club are held every 1st and 3rd Thursday of the month. We arrive at 6:30 and the meeting runs from 7:00pm to 8:45pm.
					</div>
				</details>

				<details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
					<summary class="cursor-pointer p-6 font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-between">
						<span>Where is the nearest car park?</span>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-preston-blue transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						There is plenty of free parking near the community centre off Plungington Road on Hammond Street, Preston, PR1 7EN.
					</div>
				</details>

				<details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
					<summary class="cursor-pointer p-6 font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-between">
						<span>Is the community centre wheelchair accessible?</span>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-preston-blue transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Yes, Plungington Community Centre is wheelchair friendly. We prioritise inclusivity and accessibility for all our guests and club members. The centre features ramp access, wide doorways, and wheelchair-accessible restrooms to ensure a comfortable experience for wheelchair users. If you have any specific needs or concerns, please feel free to contact us.
					</div>
				</details>

				<details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
					<summary class="cursor-pointer p-6 font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-between">
						<span>Do I need to pay if I just want to visit a meeting as a guest?</span>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-preston-blue transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						<p class="mb-4">No. We encourage anyone who just wants to try it out as a guest to come as many times as they like for free. Please feel free to reserve a spot for our next meeting.</p>
						<a href="#meetings" class="text-preston-blue hover:underline font-semibold">Join us</a>
					</div>
				</details>

				<details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
					<summary class="cursor-pointer p-6 font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-between">
						<span>What can I expect at a meeting?</span>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-preston-blue transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						<p class="mb-3">When you arrive at a meeting, you will be warmly welcomed and introduced to club members. The start of the meeting is a casual opportunity to network and get to know other guests or members of the club.</p>
						<p class="mb-3">The meeting is structured in three parts. First, there will be "Table Topics" which are short impromptu speaking opportunities for both guests and members. As a guest, we encourage you to tackle any fears and try your hand at a "Table Topic," but you can also choose to just observe if you don't feel ready.</p>
						<p class="mb-3">After a short break, the second part of the evening will be an opportunity for club members to present their prepared speeches. These speeches are longer speaking opportunities, and each one is tailored to the speaker's chosen speaking path.</p>
						<p>Finally, the last part of the meeting is for evaluations, where each speaker of the evening will receive feedback highlighting their strengths as well as areas for improvement so they can continue to grow in their abilities as an effective speaker.</p>
					</div>
				</details>

				<details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
					<summary class="cursor-pointer p-6 font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-between">
						<span>How do I become a member of Preston Speaking Club?</span>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-preston-blue transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Becoming member of the club is easy. Come as a guest for free to any meeting and ask for the Vice President of Memberships who will guide you through the membership application process.
					</div>
				</details>

				<details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
					<summary class="cursor-pointer p-6 font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 flex items-center justify-between">
						<span>What benefits do I receive once I become a member?</span>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-preston-blue transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
						</svg>
					</summary>
					<div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Joining a Toastmasters club means developing your public speaking and leadership skills, building your confidence, and getting valuable feedback on your speeches. Preston Speaking Club members have the opportunity to book in prepared speeches at club meetings, and get access to Toastmasters International educational resources to follow a personalised speaking pathway tailored to their own goals.
					</div>
				</details>

				<details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
